title: [Corsairs' Corner]
description: The battered teak dock makes an abrupt right angle turn, reducing the capacity for docking vessels somewhat.  A colorful sea glass kraken cuddled up with a bevy of merpeople has been inlaid into the center of the deck with the phrase, "Something for everyone at the Great Piratical Flotilla," carved beneath it.  Barnacle-encrusted posts and seaweed-covered bumpers mark off individual docking slips.
